Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 400
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Output gifs/tombstone.gif

Hide
Type "export PS1='user@bray:bray $ '"
Enter
Type "alias claude=./site/demos/bray-demo.sh"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show

Type "claude -p 'Use tombstone to create a deletion event for event ID d4ea1b7ffb77c1fba9b84fda4e8d838db7a39c63a9bde3962a1cb13b2c4d50e3'"
Enter
Sleep 25s
